<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Weather App</title>
    <style>
        /* Dark Theme Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            transition: background-color 0.5s, color 0.5s;
            background-image: url(''); /* Background GIF will be set here */
            background-size: cover; /* Cover entire viewport */
            background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Prevent repeating */
            background-position: center; /* Center the GIF */
        }

        a {
            color: #bb86fc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #9f69f1;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        /* Button Styles */
        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            background-color: #bb86fc;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s;
            margin-top: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #9f69f1;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }

        /* Animation Styles */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        /* Additional Styling */
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 10px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: left; /* Align text to the left */
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        {{>style}}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {{>header}} <!-- Include header partial -->
    <h1>About Our Weather App</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Welcome to the Weather App! Our mission is to provide you with accurate and up-to-date weather information to help you plan your day.</p>
        
        <p>With our application, you can:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Check the current weather for any city around the world.</li>
            <li>Get detailed weather forecasts including temperature, humidity, and wind speed.</li>
            <li>Enjoy a user-friendly interface with a beautiful dark theme.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We use the OpenWeather API to fetch real-time weather data. Thank you for using our application!</p>
        <button onclick="location.href='/'">Go back to Home</button>
    </div>

    {{>footer}} <!-- Include the footer if you have a footer partial -->
</body>
</html>
